OL,3,CMother wants extra support for parents
OL,4,Cof children with autism
OL,6,FITV News has approached the States of
OL,7,FGuernsey for a response to the issues
OL,8,Fraised.
OL,10,FNiamh McDermott runs the charity
OL,11,FAllMatters Neurodiverse Jersey which
OL,12,Fhas nearly 2,000 members in its
OL,13,FFacebook group.
OL,15,FShe says businesses should allow
OL,16,Fparents who care for neurodiverse
OL,17,Fchildren to have more flexible working
OL,18,Farrangements.
