OL,3,CMother wants extra support for parents
OL,4,Cof children with autism
OL,6,FNiamh has a child with autism and
OL,7,Fbelieves employers should be given
OL,8,Fbasic training about neurodiversity
OL,9,Fand autism.
OL,11,FShe explains: "Parents like us, we
OL,12,Fhave to keep so much patience and
OL,13,Fenergy for our children so it's very
OL,14,Fhard to have that in other areas of
OL,15,Flife."
